MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2008-0661. State v. Hunter.

Cuyahoga App. No. 89456, 2008-Ohio-794. On motion to lift stay of briefing schedule. Motion granted. The Clerk shall issue an order for the transmittal of the record from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County, and the parties shall brief this case in accordance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio.
